snippet.title: F1® Manager 2023 | Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
F1® Manager 2023, launching this summer on PC, PlayStation & Xbox!

Drive Every Decision and take on all the challenges of being an F1® team principal in the exciting new 2023 season and beyond. Choose any one of the ten teams from the 2023 championship and compete across a historic 23 races and six F1® Sprint events. Hire and develop real-world drivers and staff, build and improve your HQ, and create the next force to be reckoned with in F1®

Find out more:

Website – https://f1manager.com

Twitter – https://twitter.com/F1manager

Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/f1manager/

Facebook - https://facebook.com/f1managergame
